{"tid":1390950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 突發 ]  要人!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:01:31.000Z","uid":37529,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c00e0a82179114c942b797b80b2bedcbeb6637a5","tid":1390950,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"其實手足們一直都講<br />\n每次行動<br />\n最保護到勇武既唔係豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係木盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係人數!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n呢排連登好多奇怪風向<br />\n目標相同, 就係<strong>要減少現場參與人數</strong> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 扮關心散水論</strong></ins><br />\n尋日有個POST真係睇到火都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387877/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387877/page/1</a><br />\n標題：D後生仔又唔肯走...又死磨難磨...<br />\n內文係:唉... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有過千正評 屌晒你地老味, 可唔可以比D獨立思考呀 <br />\n<br />\n早兩日727先解釋完, 唔散係要增加警狗管治成本<br />\n令狗清場驅散一次難過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">關心擔心唔係問題</span><br />\n但係講過好多次, 請相信前線手足IQ係過80既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係理性, 會睇現場環境 TG資訊決定散唔散<br />\n我建議 如果真係擔心既<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>請推逃生路線 google map</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>請推附近屋苑4位數字</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>請推狗隻情報 最好有圖</strong></span><br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係叫人散 或者話夜啦呢類叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2. 貶低/分化勇武</strong></ins><br />\n呢兩日風向係：<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武派要停止無意義的犧牲，和理非要接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成日話要勇武 勇武完我地冇左40個手足啦!!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n成個羅輯錯撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先如果唔係前線有勇武手足, 我只可以講<strong>比狗咬既人一定唔止呢個數</strong><br />\n再講咁樣係分化緊勇武同和理非 到最後又係令人數跌<br />\n從來和理非同勇武一定要共存合作 先可以嬴<br />\n呢個唔係我地6月已經學識左既道理咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 幫警狗洗白, 同時貶低抗爭者</ins></strong><br />\n尋晚天水圍既POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1388695/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1388695/page/1</a><br />\n瘋狂幫黑狗洗白, 同時屌手足唔冷靜 講粗口好差 都仲可以過千正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部比鏡頭前既狗仔撚兩撚就收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係狗仔我都笑出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後又係制造到抗爭者唔理性既形象 意圖減少以後出席人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想Share呢個POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1390500/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1390500/page/1</a><br />\n係香港人既弱點 亦係我想講既重點<br />\n//所以大家如果真係有心想嬴，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不妨買左物資後，唔洗一次過攞晒出嚟就完，可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每一次都參與</span>，帶啲出嚟。一來大家繼續參與呢場抗爭，亦都成為流動物資站、要用拎出嚟，冇用帶返走，連物資都 be water，先至唔浪費。</span></strong>//<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3/8 旺角見!!<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ec5fe8fccbb8ec8576f94077100fc4c6ff5005d","tid":1390950,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:33:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">805三罷  如何合法癱瘓港鐵</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">和理非都可以做到！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一人一喼港鐵fashion show大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390849</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1091575861b34fba3842122c921fb5715bbae317","tid":1390950,"uid":195769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"開post還post 唔好標題黨"},{"pid":"89a9c82ac1f5eee58e622fb1d3a5790016bcbeb1","tid":1390950,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1091575861b34fba3842122c921fb5715bbae317","tid":1390950,"uid":195769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"開post還post 唔好標題黨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"sorry 可能令人誤會<br />\n但黎緊真係每一次都要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aa6928d4d018d726de921043f1ed9da67b8729","tid":1390950,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"47593c098771d5c7aa95e8320cfeadbef1910b48","tid":1390950,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"e14188ca80318f0e16250b43d027a40e7cb4b9e0","tid":1390950,"uid":195769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a9c82ac1f5eee58e622fb1d3a5790016bcbeb1","tid":1390950,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1091575861b34fba3842122c921fb5715bbae317","tid":1390950,"uid":195769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"開post還post 唔好標題黨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"sorry 可能令人誤會<br />\n但黎緊真係每一次都要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"放心 好似柯屎咁 屎到就會想柯"},{"pid":"4e8311b4e0a656b2db4bc631a957d4f9ec4aa9e9","tid":1390950,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:37:2